                        alt=""></span></span></span
              ></span>
            </p>
            <p>
              <span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;"
                ><span style="font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;"
                  ><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;"
                    ><span style="font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;"
                      ><img
                        src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0243/3030/5622/files/Group_1_1.png?v=1760965782"
                        alt=""></span></span></span
              ></span>
            </p>
            <p>
              <span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;"
                ><span style="font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;"
                  ><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;"
                    ><span style="font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;"
                      ><img
                        src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0243/3030/5622/files/GMP_1_bfb62a8d-cd83-4f67-9190-cfc06258a88f.png?v=1760965780"
                        alt=""
